&lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;I hope i'll see the day when cool features like syntactic macros or at least string interpolation will be seen in C#.
&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;My fear is, that this will happened only when Anders will ... let go. He is an extraordinary person, and C# is an extraordinary language which becomes more and more conservative as times passes....&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The same is valid about Typescript.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;But there is hope, open minded folks are in charge with F# where one sees a glimpse in what geekness can do to a language....&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
